msgctxt "1680"
msgid "Woman"
msgstr "Mujer"

msgctxt "1684"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "1688"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "68_Woman"
msgid "I just saw some men who looked like yakuza over in Theater Square!"
msgstr "¡Acabo de ver a unos hombres que parecían yakuzas en la Plaza del Teatro!"

msgctxt "80_Woman"
msgid "They were humongous! Nobody in their right mind would go anywhere near those brutes."
msgstr "¡Eran enormes! Nadie en su sano juicio se acercaría a esos tipos."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry to bother you, miss, but have you seen anyone who looks like yakuza around here lately? It would've been a group of them."
msgstr "Disculpe, lamento molestarla, pero ¿ha visto yakuzas por aquí? Varios de ellos."

msgctxt "104_Woman"
msgid "Yakuza? As a matter of fact, I just saw some men like that over in Theater Square!"
msgstr "¿Yakuzas? ¡Acabo de ver a algunos hombres así en la Plaza del Teatro!"

msgctxt "116_Woman"
msgid "They were humongous! Nobody in their right mind would go anywhere near those brutes."
msgstr "¡Eran enormes! Nadie en su sano juicio se acercaría a esos tipos."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh. Guess I'm not in my right mind, then. Anyway, thanks."
msgstr "Supongo que no estoy en mi sano juicio. De todos modos, gracias."

msgctxt "140_Woman"
msgid "Please be careful!"
msgstr "¡Por favor, tenga cuidado!"

